        "هُ رَأَى كُتُباً لِأَبِي الْحَسَنِ ( عليه السلام ) مُتَرَّبَةً ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Ali Bin Ibrahim, from his father, from Ibn Abu Umeyr, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Ali Bin Atiyya that he saw a letter of Abu Al-Hassan<sup>asws</sup> (sprinkled) with dust (to dry the ink)’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "9. Ali ibn Ibrahim has narrated from his father from ibn abu ‘Umayr from Ali ibn ‘Atiyyah who has said the following: “He had seen a soiled letter of abu al-Hassan al-Rida, recipient of divine supreme covenant.” "
        ]
